Steps to do full download:

1. Download binstallxxx.fls (open HyperTerm to see status).
2. For 2.0.4 or above, go to Manufacturing Menu, then enter Ethernet addr.
3. Do Easy Chassis Download.
	Do you want to be in CHASSIS mode ? n
 	Do you want to load the PPC file ? y
	Select ppcxxx.ld file to download.
	Do you want to erase the Application Configuration? y
	Do you want to load the board parameters? y
	Select ppcenvxxx.ld file to download.
4. Reset system and connect again to do the other non-PPC board download.
5. Do Easy Chassis Download.
	Do you want to be in CHASSIS mode ? y
	For every board 
	{
		Do you want to load board in slot 0 (DSP3)? y
		Select dsp3_xxx.ld or dvb_io_r2_xxx.ld to download.
	}
	Do you want to load the PPC file? [n]: n
	Do you want to erase the Application Configuration? [y]: y
	Do you want to load the board parameters? [n]: n


----------------

Partitions:

6 - demux for DSP3
7 - statmux for IO
27 - DPI for DSP3
2b - demux for DSP6
2c - statmux for DVOC

